<H1>OloFight Update.</H!>
</CENTER> <HR> <p><FONT SIZE="4"> 
<P>
<IMG SRC="images/oloanim2.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" ALT="Olofight screenshot">
<IMG SRC="images/oloanim1.gif" ALIGN="RIGHT" ALT="Olofight screenshot">
<FONT SIZE="6">I </FONT> brought you news of this good looking beat-em-up back
in July. Well, work on the game has been going along nicely and there should be
a playable demo available in a month or so.<P>

The game is set for an AGA only release, horever, unlike many of the games being
released now it will run on a unexpanded A1200.  The impressive part of this is
that it will keep up a frame rate of 25fps on this.<P>
<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER="3">
<TR>
<TD><IMG SRC="images/olofightup3.gif" ALT="OloFight Screenshot"></TD>
